result:
<a-modal
  :title="title"
  :visible="visible"
  :keyboard="false"
  :maskClosable="false"
  okText="保存"
  okType="primary"
  @ok="handleProcessAuditOk()"
  @cancel="handleProcessAuditCancel()">
  <a-form
    :form="form">
    <a-form-item
      label="名称"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="text"
        v-decorator="[
          'name',
          {
            rules: [
              { max:64, message: '长度在64个汉字以内' },
              {required: true, message: '请输入名称'}
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.name : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="是否合格"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="text"
        v-decorator="[
          'review_status',
          {
            rules: [
              { max:32, message: '长度在32个汉字以内' }
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.review_status : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
  </a-form>
</a-modal>
